A cyberpunk cityscape at dusk where countless glowing fiber-optic threads weave through towering dark skyscrapers, each thread splitting and multiplying into thousands of smaller luminescent strands that flow like rivers of light through the urban canyon. The threads are electric blue and purple, pulsing with energy, some converging at massive server tower structures that hum with neon accents. In the foreground, a single thick cable unravels into an impossibly dense network of gossamer-thin filaments that spread across the entire scene like a digital nervous system. Rain falls gently, catching the light from the threads and creating a misty, atmospheric glow. The perspective is looking upward from street level, emphasizing the overwhelming scale and interconnected nature of this thread network against a moody orange and purple sunset sky.
